  <p>
    Here are the problems for this assignment. The first problem comes from Section 3.1 of our textbook.  Do the second problem as written below.  For the first problem, you may use the PDF version of the book, which can be found on Blackboard under <q>Course Information &amp; Resources</q>, or you may use the online version by clicking on the link <url href="https://activecalculus.org/prelude/sec-exp-growth.html">Section 3.1</url> and scrolling down to the bottom of the page:
